== Installation

== Using cucumber
* Assuming a *nix (debian-based) dev environment.
* Install tools to compile stuff:
  apt-get install build-essential
* Install firefox.
* Install rvm and a ruby: https://rvm.beginrescueend.com/rvm/install/. Follow directions.
* Create a gemset to hold the cucumber environment:
  rvm gemset create cucumber
	rvm gemset use cucumber
* If on linux, install dependencies to satisify needed gems:
  apt-get install libxslt1-dev libxml2-dev libxml2 libxslt1.1 openjdk-6-jre
* install bundler, which'll bootstrap the rest of the installation:
  rvm install bundler
* cd into the directory containing the "Gemfile" and then:
  bundle install



